title: Switchblade Symphony - Sweet Live Witches
description:
The long-awaited concert DVD from the seductive sisters of sinister sweetness, Switchblade Symphony! Recorded at various concerts in 1997 - 1999 and includes performances of Clown, Witches, Drool, Dirty Dog and other fan favorites!


Seductive, flirtatious, always commanding, no one gives good show like the sultry sirens of Switchblade Symphony. Since their arrival nearly a decade ago, not a single band on the scene has been able to top the girls in terms of sheer originality and mesmerizing darkwave charm. With fans drooling over their Sweet Little Witches live CD in '03, it's clear now that was only the foreplay. This luscious visual scrap book is the payoff for all who long to see their favorite goth goddesses cast that glittery spell on stage once again. Enhanced by multiple angles and exotic locales, Tina, Susan and the rest of the coven invite you into their circle of sonic bliss. --Cleopatra Records
